#: personalpostexporter.php
msgid "Personal Post Exporter"
msgstr "Personal Post Exporter"

#: personalpostexporter.php
msgid "With this exporter, you can download your own archive from your Friendica instance. You will receive a ZIP file containing your posts arranged in a blog-like style. A search function is also included."
msgstr "With this exporter, you can download your own archive from your Friendica instance. You will receive a ZIP file containing your posts arranged in a blog-like style. A search function is also included."

#: personalpostexporter.php
msgid "IMPORTANT:"
msgstr "IMPORTANT:"

#: personalpostexporter.php
msgid "This archive is for viewing and searching only. It is not a technical backup and cannot be used to re-import your posts into another Friendica instance if you move your account."
msgstr "This archive is for viewing and searching only. It is not a technical backup and cannot be used to re-import your posts into another Friendica instance if you move your account."

